Package mil.nga.giat.geowave.ingest.hdfs

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    HdfsPluginBase
    All plugins based off of staged intermediate data (either reading or writing) must implement this interface.
    StageToHdfsPlugin<T>
    This is the main plugin interface for reading from a local file system, and staging intermediate data to HDFS from any file that is supported.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractStageFileToHdfs
    This class can be sub-classed as a general-purpose recipe for parallelizing ingestion of files by directly staging the binary of the file to HDFS.
    HdfsCommandLineOptions
    This class encapsulates the command-line options and parsed values specific to staging intermediate data to HDFS.
    HdfsFile  
    HdfsFile.Builder
    RecordBuilder for HdfsFile instances.
    StageRunData
    A class to hold intermediate stage data that must be used throughout the life of the HDFS stage process.
    StageToHdfsDriver
    This class actually executes the staging of data to HDFS based on the available type plugin providers that are discovered through SPI.
